AlnClusWeight.

  This program calculates a weight for each sequence in a MSA according to the
  size of the sequence cluster it belong. The weight is calculated as 1 / size
  of cluster. Clustering is performed with Hobohm-1 method. 
  
Usage:
  alnclusweight.jar <Options>  
 
Options:
  --infile      Path file to input alignment. If omitted standard input is used.
  
  --outfile     Path file to output file. If omitted standard output is used.
                
  --clusterId   Real Number. Identity fraction threshold for sequence clustering. 
                By default 0.62 is used.

  --help        Shows this help and exits.
